Usage: report_parameter [-help] [-correlation] [-name <string>]
                        -scope {vtskew wire_variation beol lle layout_effect}
                        -view <string>

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-correlation       # report correlation (bool, optional)
-name <string>     # parameter name (string, optional)
-scope {vtskew wire_variation beol lle layout_effect}
                   # parameter scope ( vtskew|wire_variation ) (enum, required)
-view <string>     # View name (string, required)